data.description: Welcome to 2930 Greenbriar Lane! This move-in ready home features stunning cathedral ceilings, four bedrooms, two baths, two bonus rooms AND a formal dining room!!! The recent updates on this home include lifetime warranty windows and double ovens less than five years old. The master bath shower, paint, lights and mirrors are all under a year old along with all of the laminate flooring and the roof, dishwasher, and master carpet were replaced in 2022!!!  Along with the updates, this home boasts tons of storage space BOTH inside and out with not only one, but THREE storage sheds in the backyard. Take refuge in the shade under the mature oak trees that sit on this just shy of an acre property.  This is quiet country living close to everything. Make this one yours today!!!
